                     <interp inst="t18190217-70-person722" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am servant to the prosecutor. I was in the back-room watching, and saw the prisoner put the shoes into his pocket.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. Distress drove me to it.</p>
